{"tid":883734,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"未來見呢首歌真係屈機到仆咗街","createTime":"2018-10-31T05:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T12:20:22.000Z","uid":136116,"like":102,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aef3e91fbad84d8b4b9acbb7f580209385f6e3cc","tid":883734,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"首先取材方面已經贏撚咗 依家香港樂壇10首歌有9首都係講愛情 呢首歌定位定係兄弟情 已經好吸引<br />\n好過啲dear jane 每首都講自己溝女咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住主唱把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點解唱出嚟嘅感覺好甜 好暖心 真係諗返起自己中學同班friend日日搞gay啲往事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚懷念<br />\n好特別仲有一句: 從雨裏高唱的 回音尚有<br />\n個回字個下沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次聽聽到起晒雞皮 正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個節奏又好鮮明好易入腦 intro out-tro 都好撚正 個歌詞都好有韻味好雋永<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正式宣佈呢首歌係今年金曲金獎得主 不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad74dad98fed43065cca6db39b02875a260ea57","tid":883734,"uid":27564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"成首曲正唔在講, 個人十分喜歡嗰段差唔多長一分鐘既outro,好有畫面感, 6號既ad-libs 同阿正手結他, 令我真係有&quot;千帆過後, 仍然與你一起看夕陽&quot;既畫面出現係腦海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (MV更加加強左呢個效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ffd5726e99480d0e74e9c2d59efdd2c5f2ed9ef0","tid":883734,"uid":69568,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"6號把聲真係暖到仆街 一開始 阿波羅 同simplelovesong同夏令時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm